The paper deals with theoretical results on the generalization properties of learning algorithms for multiclass classification problems. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
